{"tid":1671983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[別忘記] 大埔斬人案","createTime":"2019-10-23T23:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T00:33:31.000Z","uid":61520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0238965ac17c041a961de32ccfc5eea189b06239","tid":1671983,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:59:15.000Z","msg":"大埔發生斬人案，下午5時許，有街坊於大埔連儂隧道派發周日九龍大遊行的傳單，一名黑衫男子將牆上的memo紙撕下，其間與街坊爭執，黑衫男突然取出一把長約20厘米的生果刀，襲擊一名19歲姓熊青年的頸部，傷者倒地後，狂徒再上前向其腹部刺多刀，腸臟外露，狂徒逞兇後登上的士離去。警方其後接報到場，將傷者送往沙田威爾斯醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191019&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60172810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191019%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60172810&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b4e1265b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191019%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60172810&h=df0d10a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191019&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60172810</a>"},{"pid":"ed069d8d237275323983dbdcec09a7ddd9da6f32","tid":1671983,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:59:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66f4666726e57d7571140eaa302a1f2192514ea6","tid":1671983,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"7526e5844149e814dd6b80e5987464a8166b620e","tid":1671983,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"推二"},{"pid":"9878abf61a9fb19edf8c10e11684cab7960114b1","tid":1671983,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88d0783d801137d14c4071c6b4d2105ed7167a77","tid":1671983,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:33:31.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=